{"tid":2426834,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨政府：透過安心出行追蹤到70至80宗個案大成功 稱未能判斷身份有限制 要加強監控","createTime":"2021-02-28T11:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T11:44:32.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0205a4e7d7eb92d7fa453737f6e90a0ef170f74a","tid":2426834,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T11:00:33.000Z","msg":"歐家榮稱至今透過安心出行追蹤到70至80宗個案<br />\n<br />\nK11 MUSEA的新型肺炎感染群組進一步擴大，再多10宗確診，累計錄得44宗感染個案。衞生防護中心首席醫生歐家榮表示，已就K11 MUSEA名潮食館的感染通知，透過「安心出行」應用程式發放，如有人曾與確診個案於同一時間在有關食肆出現，就會收到通知。<br />\n<br />\n歐家榮指出，當局至今透過「安心出行」追蹤到70至80宗個案，形容程式有用但亦有限制，例如只有食客收到通知，但當局無法知道對方身份，因此仍有部分個案未能追蹤到，相信有關部分會研究如何提升程式的效能。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577979-20210228.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577979-20210228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3vno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=5ef80c3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577979-20210228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=affee649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577979-20210228.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"781bb167821682f65a1e0c3def6dcd2cb48acb82","tid":2426834,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T11:01:53.000Z","msg":"裝左app既人係咪同黃世澤評論一樣戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n=========================================<br />\n簽名檔<br />\n<br />\n[戇鳩警報器: 黃世澤 | martin oei | 交加街38號 ] 警世 黃世澤係令大家用唔到BNO移民既始作俑者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2423877\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2423877</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"320a1e6ae7d9f1fc9b681d9259037b95e7cae99c","tid":2426834,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T11:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a519737734fb740496859215c18d16fa5c4